description: This is the main entry point for a React web application. It imports React and ReactDOM libraries, along with CSS styles and the main App component. It creates a React root and renders the App component within a StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root element for rendering the React component tree.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
